Help for the PEDIT01 editor

Line Commands:
--------------

Extensions to the normal ISPF PDF editor line commands:
MNn      Make note.  Turn current line(s) into note lines, shown by =NOTE=
MNN

TJn      Text join.  Join a number of lines (default 1) togeter separated by a space

TXn      Toggle exclude status of a line/block of lines
TXX

XP       Exclude paragraph.  Exclude lines until the indentation is less than the indentation where the command
         is entered.
